rev.desc.rev.desc: Don't update stathistory unless we really change a value. Don't error exit on known common error conditions that occur during load testing - radd duplicate key error, rupdate record has been changed error.

Changes to support licesne to DB project. No longer call set.module.license() multiple times if the RTE can accept all the values in an array. Also make code backward compatibile. Stathistory changes to skip updates if record not changed and ignore error on radd/rupdate calls since it's not important and prevents login.
Do not throw error out, only log the error informaiton . Change the panel: exit.error.msg
